 information.",privacyMetaKeywords:"Privacy Policy, Pixel Morph, Free Online Image Processing, Data Protection",heroTitle:"AI Face Shape Detector – Detect Face Shape Instantly ",heroDescription:"Want to know which styles suit you best? Our AI Face Shape Detector makes it easy to find your face shape and get simple, personalized ideas for hairstyles, makeup, and more, so you can feel confident in every look.",timesLeftToday:"Times Left Today",unlockMoreTemplates:"Unlock More Face Shape Detector Templates",scanToDownload:"Scan to Download",instantFaceSwap:"Instant Face Shape Detector",realisticSeamlessFaceSwaps:"Realistic & Seamless Face Shape Detectors",makeFunPhotos:"Make Photos Fun with AI FaceSwap Online",transformIntoFamousArt:"Transform Yourself into Famous Art with AI Face Shape Detectorper",uploadSourcePhoto:"Upload Source Photo",chooseTargetPhoto:"Choose Target Photo",faceSwapNow:"Face Shape Detector Now",latestFromOurBlog:"Latest From Our Blog",whatCanAIFaceSwapperDo:"Quick and Easy Face Shape Finder",feature1Title:"AI Face Shape Detector for Fast and Accurate Analysis",feature1Description:"Upload a photo and let our advanced face shape detector analyze your facial structure using smart AI technology. With precise facial mapping, it quickly identifies your face type and gives you personalized insights—simple, reliable, and tech-powered.",feature2Title:"Your Privacy Comes First",feature2Description:"Worried about uploading personal photos online? Our face shape analysis is built with privacy in mind. All images are processed securely, and no data is stored or shared. With end-to-end encryption, your photos stay protected—so you can use the tool confidently and without worry.",feature3Title:"Upload or take a photo, and the face shape detector does the rest",feature3Description:"Upload or take a photo, and the face shape detector does the rest—analyzing your features instantly to find your face shape and suggest styles that suit you best. Whether you're curious about your look or choosing the right hairstyle or glasses, this tool makes it simple. Fast, accurate, and completely beginner-friendly.",feature4Title:"Personalized Hair and Makeup Tips Just for You",feature4Description:"Using your photo as input, the face type detector analyzes your unique features, from face size to eye, lip, Jawline, and nose shape, to provide custom styling suggestions. Get tailored hair and makeup advice that suits your face perfectly, all in seconds.",perfectFaceSwapperForEveryone:"Best Face Shape Analyzer",perfectFaceSwapperDescription:"Using advanced analysis, the face shape detection tool quickly determine your face shape type, whether it's round face, oval face, heart-shaped face, Oblong face, or square face. It then offers personalized hair and makeup tips designed to match your unique features and enhance your natural look.",singlePerfectFaceSwapperSections:[{title:"Detect Your Eye Shape",description:"Struggling to choose the right eye makeup? Our smart tool works alongside the face shape analysis feature to detect face shape and your eye shape, size, and spacing. It even identifies under-eye areas to recommend makeup styles that truly suit your natural features",image:"/images/detect face shape.webp",alt:"Detect Your Eye Shape",bgColor:"from-sky-200 to-sky-50",bgColorDark:"bg-sky-100"},{title:"Choose the Right Lipstick Shade for Your Shape",description:"Not sure which lipstick shade is right for you? Our face shape checker analyzes your unique facial features to recommend colors that naturally flatter your look, making it easier to choose shades that truly suit you.",image:"/images/Face Shape detector.webp",alt:"Choose the Right Lipstick Shade for Your Shape",bgColor:"from-amber-300 to-amber-50",bgColorDark:"bg-amber-100"},{title:"Analyze Your Nose Shape with AI Precision",description:"Your nose plays a key role in defining your overall facial balance. With the help of our face shape detector AI, you can identify whether your nose is narrow, wide, or somewhere in between, along with personalized tips for contouring and makeup that suit your unique features.",image:"/images/find my face shape.webp",alt:"Analyze Your Nose Shape with AI Precision",bgColor:"from-pink-300 to-pink-100",bgColorDark:"bg-pink-50"},{title:"Find the Best Eyebrow Shape for Your Face",description:"Using insights from the online face shape detector, this tool reviews your facial structure and eyebrow details to recommend brow shapes that truly suit you. Get tailored suggestions that highlight your features and complement your natural look.",image:"/images/Eyebrow Shape.webp",alt:"Find the Best Eyebrow Shape for Your Face",bgColor:"from-pink-300 to-pink-100",bgColorDark:"bg-pink-50"}],howToUseFaceSwap:"How To Use AI Face Shape Detector?",singleHowToUseSteps:[{icon:"upload",title:"Upload a photo",description:"Use the button below to select an image or take a photo"},{icon:"image",title:"Scan & Analyze",description:"The AI will automatically detect and analyze the face shape along with other features in the photo"},{icon:"click",title:"Check Results",description:"You can review your face shape analysis along with personalized recommendations."}],allOnlinePhotoVideoEditingTools:"All Online Photo & Video Editing Tools",tryItNow:"Try it now",singleTools:[{title:"AI Face Shape Detector",description:"AI Face Shape Detector lets you easily swap faces in any photo. With a few clicks, create fun or creative images and experience endless possibilities with face transformations.",image:"/multi/img1.webp",alt:"AI Face Shape Detector before and after comparison"},{title:"Multiple Face Shape Detector AI",description:"Multiple Face Shape Detector AI lets you swap multiple faces in a single image with ease. Perfect for group photos, it creates fun, shareable results in just a few clicks.",image:"/multi/1.webp",alt:"Multiple Face Shape Detector AI before and after comparison"}],userReviews:"USER REVIEWS",userReviewsData:[{name:"Jasmine Monroe",rating:"★★★★★",review:"I've tried a few face tools before, but this one is by far the most accurate. It nailed my face shape and even recommended the perfect hairstyle I never thought would suit me. Super helpful and surprisingly fun to use!"},{name:"Caleb Turner",rating:"★★★★★",review:"As a content creator, this tool saved me time and guesswork. The face shape suggestions are spot on, and I loved how it guided me on what beard style works best for my face. Totally worth using before your next makeover."},{name:"Emily Sanders",rating:"★★★★★",review:"I had no idea what my actual face shape was until I used this tool. Turns out I've been using the wrong makeup contour this whole time! The tips felt really tailored, like having a personal stylist in your pocket."}],faceShapeTypesTitle:"Hairstyle Ideas for Every Face Shape",faceShapeTypesSubtitle:"Discover hairstyles that flatter your face shape. Upload a photo to detect face shape and get personalized hairstyle recommendations for men and women.",faceShapes:[{name:"Round",mensHairstyle:["Short sides with volume on top","Textured quiff","Side-parted styles"],womensHairstyle:["Long layers","Side-swept bangs","High ponytails"]},{name:"Square",mensHairstyle:["Crew cut","Short textured crop","Slicked-back styles"],womensHairstyle:["Soft waves","Curtain bangs","Long layered cuts"]},{name:"Oval",mensHairstyle:["Buzz cut","Pompadour","Side part"],womensHairstyle:["Blunt bob","Long waves","Pixie cut"]},{name:"Heart",mensHairstyle:["Medium-length styles with side sweep","Textured fringe"],womensHairstyle:["Chin-length bob","Curtain/side bangs","Loose waves"]},{name:"Diamond",mensHairstyle:["Fringe","Side-parted medium styles","Slight volume on sides"],womensHairstyle:["Shoulder-length cuts","Textured bobs","Deep side parts"]},{name:"Oblong",mensHairstyle:["Shorter sides with moderate top volume","Side-swept bangs","Textured crop or fringe to shorten face"],womensHairstyle:["Shoulder-length or layered cuts","Side-swept bangs","Wavy or curly styles to add width"]}],differentFaceTypesTitle:"Face Shape Types",differentFaceTypesSubtitle:"The six most common face shapes",differentFaceTypes:[{name:"Oval",description:"An oval face shape is characterized by balanced proportions where the face length is slightly longer than its width. The forehead is typically wider than the jawline, with softly rounded edges and a gently tapered chin. An oval shaped face is commonly described as even and symmetrical."},{name:"Round",description:"A round face shape has a similar width and length with soft, curved lines. The cheeks are usually full, and the jawline is smooth rather than sharp. A round shaped face often appears balanced and youthful, with fewer angles and a gently rounded overall appearance."},{name:"Heart",description:"A heart face shape is wider at the forehead and gradually narrows toward the chin. The cheekbones are often noticeable, and the chin may appear pointed. A heart shaped face creates a top-heavy appearance with a softer, slimmer lower face and clear facial contrast."},{name:"Diamond",description:"A diamond face shape has a narrow forehead and jawline with wide, prominent cheekbones. The face appears angular, with sharper lines and a slightly pointed chin. A diamond shaped face is less common and is defined by strong cheekbone structure and balanced facial length."},{name:"Square",description:"A square face shape has strong, straight lines with similar width across the forehead, cheekbones, and jawline. The jaw is usually broad and well defined, creating a structured look. This face shape often appears balanced and angular, with clear edges rather than soft curves."},{name:"Oblong",description:"An oblong face shape is longer than it is wide, with a straight cheek line and a narrow jaw. The forehead, cheeks, and jaw are usually similar in width. This face shape has a long, slim appearance with fewer curves and a more rectangular overall outline."}],frequentlyAskedQuestions:"Frequently Asked Questions",faqQuestions:{q1:"How can I detect my face shape with this tool?",a1:"Simply upload or take a photo, and the tool will automatically detect your face shape using advanced AI. It analyzes key facial points to give you a clear shape match in seconds.",q2:"Is the face shape detection accurate?",a2:"Yes! The tool uses advanced algorithms for accurate face shape detection, ensuring results that reflect your true facial structure—even with different angles or lighting.",q3:"Can this help me choose a suitable hairstyle?",a3:"Absolutely. The face shape detector and hairstyle suggestions work together to recommend styles that flatter your natural shape, whether you're looking for a haircut or hair makeover.",q4:"Do I need to download anything to use it?",a4:"No downloads required. This is an online face shape detector, so you can use it directly from your browser on desktop or mobile.",q5:"Can I use this tool for free?",a5:"Yes! The tool includes features like AI face analysis free, letting you explore your face shape and get personalized tips without any cost.",q6:"How does the tool identify my face shape?",a6:"The face shape identifier maps your facial landmarks—like forehead, cheekbones, and jawline—and then runs a quick face shape analysis to classify your shape.",q7:"What if I'm not sure about my face type?",a7:"Just ask the tool to find my face shape, and it will do the rest. It's a powerful face shape checker that provides clear, visual results even if you're unsure where to start.",q8:"Is this tool beginner-friendly?",a8:"Definitely! Whether you're using it to detect face shape for styling or just out of curiosity, the tool is designed for ease of use, perfect for both casual users and style enthusiasts."},footerCompany:"Pixocial",footerCompanyDescription:"The world leading tech company in digital content and GenAI.",featuresAndTools:"Features & Tools",uploadMultipleFaces:"Upload Multiple Faces",groupPhoto:"Group Photo",swapAllFaces:"Swap All Faces",unlo